original_title: Planet Heroes - The Ace That Jumped Over The Moon
overview: Fisher Price Planet Heroes The Ace that jumped over the moon Earth Ace and his need for speed land him on the Moon--and into an instant friendship with Moon "Lunar", Sun's old friend. When Ace receives a distress call from Sun "commander", Moon decides to help Ace and his old pal fight the forces of Black Hole "professor Darkness". The rest of the Planet Hero's team is immobilized, so what can they do? With Secret Weapon named "Lola" (a space cow!), the two head into a battle you won't want to miss! Approx.16 minute episode * Color * Not Rated
title: Planet Heroes - The Ace That Jumped Over The Moon
